videos.description: Omari Spellman sinks the jumper after coming up with a steal.
videos.headline: Villanova's Spellman's steal leads to fade-away bucket

videos.description: Jacob Larsen draws the foul while hitting a contested layup.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Larsen hits tough layup and draws foul

videos.description: Mikal Bridges sinks the 3-pointer off a kick out pass from Donte DiVincenzo.
videos.headline: Villanova's Bridges knocks down 3

videos.description: Phil Booth jumps the Gonzaga pass and finishes with a big time dunk.
videos.headline: Villanova's Booth puts down fast-break slam after steal.

videos.description: Phil Booth hits a tough layup after using a smooth shot fake.
videos.headline: Villanova's Booth sets up layup with shot fake

videos.description: Phil Booth, Mikal Bridges, and Donte DiVincenzo sink 3-pointers on three straight possessions for Villanova.
videos.headline: Villanova knocks down back-to-back-to-back 3s

videos.description: Jalen Brunson drives and picks up the foul while still putting in the layup.
videos.headline: Villanova's Brunson draws foul on tough layup

videos.description: After Mikal Bridges rejects Killian Tillie, Donte DiVincenzo finds Jalen Brunson who finishes with layup.
videos.headline: Bridges' block leads to Villanova fast-break score

videos.description: Eric Pashall passes to Phil Booth flying into the lane who finishes with a big dunk.
videos.headline: Villanova's Booth puts down two-handed slam

videos.description: Villanova's Mikal Bridges speaks with Holly Rowe after scoring a career high 28-points against Gonzaga.
videos.headline: Bridges credits career night to teammates

videos.description: Mikal Bridges drops a career-high 28 points and Phil Booth ties a career-high with 20 as Villanova rolls past Gonzaga 88-72.
videos.headline: Bridges, Nova handle Gonzaga

videos.description: After a career night at Madison Garden, Mikal Bridges says his job as the leader and senior captain for Villanova is to "set the tone defensively."

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Bridges looked to set tone on defense) 2017/12/05
